#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to display icons (reminder, recursion &etc;) in Agenda view "
"items"
msgstr ""
"Agenda view items मध्ये चिह्नानि (reminder, recursion &etc;) प्रदर्शयितुं एतत् पेटी "
